MATH KIDS - OPERATIONS Privacy Policy

Math Kids ios does not collect any data from the user of any sorts. 

Data within the app like the amount of times you have practiced a day is stored on the device and IS NEVER moved of the device.

This data is not shared with anyone and can be deleted by the user by clicking the reset button in the settings page of the aplication. 

